cs.DC, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.Distributed, cs.AI 

The paper discusses fault tolerance in distributed deep learning, which involves parallel computing and large-scale data analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also focuses on deep learning algorithms and their properties, which suggests categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper discusses fault tolerance proposals in MPI, which falls under the category of cs.Distributed. Finally, the paper's focus on deep learning and its applications suggests a possible category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
